{"tid":348711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩名中國遊客柏林做納粹敬禮被捕","createTime":"2017-08-06T03:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T03:09:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a515a47e67a0bc7362c65024f5e0348cbe3a5d60","tid":348711,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在德國柏林，兩名中國遊客因為做出違法的納粹敬禮手勢被捕，兩人獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n兩名分別36歲和49歲的中國遊客，周六在柏林的國會大樓前被指做出納粹敬禮手勢，更以手機拍照留念，兩人其後因為使用非法組織符號的罪名，被警方拘捕，經查問後獲准以500歐元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n德國嚴禁使用有關納粹德國和領袖希特勒的口號和符號，一經定罪最高可被判入獄三年。"},{"pid":"abe5a42fa9e4d3af43768af3ee93bf55f1d0559a","tid":348711,"uid":15977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"又一個呃正評post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f65daacfd810ae70c2cec5bc7b8b5224728f83","tid":348711,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}